  "biography": "Kelly Rossum is an international trumpet artist, improviser and composer. He has performed everything from lead trumpet at New York\u2019s famed Birdland jazz club to baroque trumpet in Bad S\u00e4ckingen, Germany; and from improvised free jazz in Bangkok, Thailand to traditional Son in Santiago de Cuba. His original compositions, incorporating improvisational and contemporary avant-garde techniques, have been commissioned, performed and recorded by individual artists and large organizations alike. He has provided original scores for both film and dance and has received support from the American Composers Forum and the Jerome Foundation.",
  "education_entries": [
